d30 99
a128 47
  /*************************************************************************/
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Section>                                                             */
  /*    cache_subsystem                                                    */
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Title>                                                               */
  /*    Cache Sub-System                                                   */
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Abstract>                                                            */
  /*    How to cache face, size, and glyph data with FreeType 2.           */
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Description>                                                         */
  /*   This section describes the FreeType 2 cache sub-system which is     */
  /*   stile in beta.                                                      */
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Order>                                                               */
